posts.text: 1-min read David Moyes Takes Over at West Ham United After Bilic Exit West Ham United have appointed David Moyes as their manager following the sacking of Slaven Bilic, the Premier League club said on Tuesday. Updated: November 7, 2017, 2:52 PM IST David Moyes. (Getty Images) West Ham United have appointed David Moyes as their manager following the sacking of Slaven Bilic, the Premier League club said on Tuesday. Croatian Bilic was sacked on Monday following a meeting with club officials as West Ham dropped into the relegation zone after a 4-1 home defeat by Liverpool left them with two wins in 11 league games. "It's a big job we have in hand now but I'm sure with everybody together we can get the right results between now and the end of the season," Moyes said in a video on West Ham's Twitter account. West Ham United can confirm the appointment of David Moyes as the Club’s manager. pic.twitter.com/AIOWnHWn27 — West Ham United (@WestHamUtd) November 7, 2017 Moyes who was in India during the FIFA U-17 World Cup as part of the expert panel on the official broadcast, was the manager of the now relegated Sunderland last season and had stepped down at the end of the season. Prior to that he was with Real Sociedad in Spain where he was shown the door after continued dismal performances. Moyes – also called ‘The Chosen One’ when he replaced the inimitable Sir Alex Ferguson at Manchester United, could not survive the full 2013/14 season at Old Trafford. The former Everton man’s first assignment with the beleaguered West Ham United will be away at Watford after the international break on November 19.

posts.text:
Ana Sayfa » Türkiye 07.11.2017 12:23 Manisa'da Milliyetçi Hareket Partisi (MHP) Şehzadeler İlçe Başkanı Şener Özten'e ait iş yerinin vitrini gece yarısı kimliği belirsiz bir kişi tarafından... 
Manisa'da Milliyetçi Hareket Partisi (MHP) Şehzadeler İlçe Başkanı Şener Özten'e ait iş yerinin vitrini gece yarısı kimliği belirsiz bir kişi tarafından kurşunlandı. 
Olay, gece 02.30 sıralarında Manisa'nın Şehzadeler ilçesine bağlı Utku Mahallesi'nde meydana geldi. Edinilen bilgiye göre, MHP Şehzadeler İlçe Başkanı Şener Özten'e ait film satışı yapılan dükkanın vitrinine kimliği belirsiz bir kişi tarafından tüfekle yakından 2 el ateş edildi. Ateş sonucu boş olan dükkanın vitrin camı parçalandı. Ateş açan saldırgan ise olay yerinden kaçarken, olayı gören çevredekilerin haber vermesi üzerine polis ekipleri sevk edildi. Olay Yeri İnceleme ekipleri tarafından başlatılan çalışmalar tamamlanırken, polis şimdi her yerde saldırgan şahsı arıyor. 
"ARKADAN NE ÇIKACAĞINA BAKACAĞIZ" 
Yaşanan olayla ilgili konuşan MHP Şehzadeler İlçe Başkanı Şener Özten, "Gece saat 22.30 sıralarında iş yerimi kapatıp evime geçtim. Sabah da dükkan komşularım aradı. Camda bir delik olduğunu söylediler. Sağ olsun polis ekipleri ilgilendi. Olay yeri inceleme ekipleri geldi. Her halde tahminimce tüfekle iki sefer ateş edilmiş gece 01.30-02.30 arasında. Çevredekiler duymuş. Polis arkadaşlar incelemeleri yapıyorlar. İnşallah failleri kısa sürede yakalanır. Komşulardan görenler var. 1 kişi yakından mesafeden cama sıkıyor ve kaçıyor. Kasıt olduğunu düşünmüyorum. Kimseyle bir husumetimiz yok. Allah'a şükür 25 senedir esnafız burada. Arkadan ne çıkacağına bakacağız" dedi. 
(Aykut Yeniçağ /İHA)

posts.text: Email This Story Printer Friendly PDF Version RSS Feed Visix Hotel Wayfinding Design Wins Davey Award for Best User Experience Visix, Inc. has been honored with a Silver Davey Award for their custom wayfinding design for Crowne Plaza Atlanta Midtown. User experience is what wayfinding is all about, and our team works hard to marry the customer vision with the best design and navigation possible. ATLANTA, GA,   Visix, Inc. has been honored with a Silver Davey Award for their custom wayfinding design for Crowne Plaza Atlanta Midtown. The award is in the feature category of Best User Experience, recognizing superior design and navigation as a whole. The project was commissioned by Crowne Plaza to assist guests in locating meetings and events within the hotel. It includes interactive wayfinding and an events directory fed by the hotel's Delphi database tied to floor maps. The custom design spotlights the organization's branding, and was created using HTML5, so the entire wayfinding project is responsive for mobile devices. "We're thrilled to have won an award in this brand-new category," says Jill Perardi, Creative Services Manager for Visix. "User experience is what wayfinding is all about, and our team works hard to marry the customer vision with the best design and navigation possible. User experience is especially important in hotel wayfinding, since you're reaching all types of viewers. We're honored that the Davey Awards has recognized our efforts." The Visix Creative Services team has been honored with over 90 awards for their digital signage designs. For more information about Visix wayfinding design services, visit www.visix.com/products/interactive-packages . About the Davey Awards The Davey Awards honors the finest creative work from the best small agencies, firms, and companies worldwide. The awards are judged and overseen by the Academy of Interactive and Visual Arts (AIVA). Visit www.daveyawards.com for the list of winners. About Visix Visix, Inc. designs, develops and supports a suite of browser-based digital signage products that allows users to create, manage and schedule organizational communications from anywhere and to deliver messages, media and alerts to virtually any endpoint. The company offers digital signage software, award-winning content design, meeting room signs, and applications for targeted messaging to desktops and personal devices. » Finance Ini Masukan Penting dari Pengusaha Agar Pelabuhan Batam Bisa Bersaing dengan Singapura-Malaysia Dalam beleid ini, menurut Bani Maulana, tarif pelabuhan lebih tinggi 0,1 dolar AS ketimbang di Singapura dan Malaysia.   15:59 tribunbatam/aminnudin Proses bongkar muat kontainer di Pelabuhan Kijang. Foto sebagai ilustrasi berita. 
TRIBUNBATAM.ID- Badan Pengusahaan (BP) Batam telah memiliki nakhoda baru lengkap dengan para deputinya. 
Satu hal yang menjadi perhatian pengusaha bagi BP Batam agar dapat diperbaiki adalah tentang fasilitas pelabuhan. 
Sebab, Pelabuhan menjadi fasilitas perhubungan penting di wilayah kepulauan. 
Masih terkendalanya aktivitas pelabuhan di Batam menjadi salah satu fokus kinerja Badan Pengusahaan (BP) Batam yang baru. 
Harapan sejumlah pengusaha untuk pembenahan Pelabuhan Batam pun bisa menjadi masukan bagi BP Batam. Bani Maulana Mulia selaku Managing Director PT Samudera Indonesia, Tbk. (kontan) 
Bani Maulana Mulia selaku Managing Director PT Samudera Indonesia, Tbk (SMDR) menilai, isu yang perlu dipertimbangkan ialah Peraturan Kepala (Perka) No. 17 tahun 2016. 
Dalam beleid ini, menurut dia, tarif pelabuhan lebih tinggi 0,1 dolar AS ketimbang di Singapura dan Malaysia. 
Selain itu, pemberlakuannya tanpa waktu sosialisasi maupun adaptasi yang cukup. 
"Ini yang membuat daya saing pelabuhan Batam menjadi turun dan berat bagi pengusaha," kata Bani kepada Kontan.co.id, Selasa (7/11). 
Carmelita Hartoto, Ketua DPP Indonesian National Shipowners Association (INSA) bilang pihaknya tengah berdiskusi dengan berbagai asosiasi lain untuk memberikan masukan terkait permasalahan pelabuhan. 
"Kami sedang diskusi dengan pemerintah mengenai tarif-tarif kepelabuhan dan beberapa kebijakan yang dianggap kurang pas," jelas Carmelita. (kontan/Ramadhani Prihatini)

NGT Pulls Up State Govts A bench headed by NGT Chairperson Justice Swatanter Kumar lambasted the state governments of Delhi, Uttar Pradesh and Haryana for not being prepared in advance to tackle the emergency pollution situation. Updated: November 10, 2017, 12:33 PM IST Delhi woke up this morning to "severe" air quality under a blanket of thick haze. New Delhi: As the national capital reeled under heavy smog, the National Green Tribunal on Tuesday took the governments of Delhi, Uttar Pradesh and Haryana to task and asked them to explain why preventive steps were not taken to control the ‘severe’ air quality in the region. A bench headed by NGT Chairperson Justice Swatanter Kumar lambasted the state governments for not being prepared in advance to tackle the emergency situation. Delhi woke up this morning to ‘severe’ air quality under a blanket of thick haze, as pollution levels breached the permissible standards by multiple times. he Central Pollution Control Board (CPCB) recorded ‘severe’ air quality, meaning that the intensity of pollution was extreme. “The ambient air quality is so bad that children are not able to breath properly. Why didn’t you not spray water using helicopters as per our direction? You take instructions and inform us day after tomorrow,” the bench said. It asked the state governments to explain why they had not taken preventive and precautionary measures as it was reported earlier that such a situation was likely to arise. The green panel also directed the CPCB to state what emergency directions it has issued in excercise of its powers to tackle the situation. The tribunal was hearing a plea for immediate action against the worsening air quality in Delhi-NCR stating that it was an ‘environmental emergency' which was affecting children and senior citizens the most. The plea said that according to CPCB report, post Diwali the ambient air quality of Delhi on October 17, 18 and 19 was found to be “very poor”. The plea also said that despite such elaborate orders from the NGT last year, the authorities have slept over it. Highlighting the increasing number of cars in the city, the plea filed by environment activist Akash Vashishta said it was “imperative that the government should take a view” with regards to putting a cap on vehicles to reduce air pollution. The plea has also sought direction to Delhi and the neighbouring states to file a status report with regard to the steps taken to educate people regarding waste burning and the pollution caused by it.

New Delhi: On a day when Delhi woke up to a thick cover of smog and worrying levels of air pollution, Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal asked his deputy and Education Minister Manish Sisodia to consider shutting schools for a few days in the city. "Considering high level of pollution, I have requested Manish Sisodia, Education Minister, to consider closing schools for few days," Kejriwal tweeted. The Indian Medical Association (IMA) has also appealed to the Delhi government to shut down outdoor sports and other such activities in schools keeping in view the harmful impact of air pollution on the health of the children. The rapid fall in air quality and visibility began on Monday evening as moisture combined with pollutants shrouded the city in a thick cover of haze. With the morning air reaching severe levels, it has become all the more hazardous for school and college students and office goers. By 10 am on Tuesday, the Central Pollution Control Board (CPCB) recorded 'severe' air quality, meaning the intensity of pollution was extreme. While an Air Quality Index (AQI) between 0-50 is considered good, Delhi’s average AQI was 411 at 9am on Tuesday morning, which is read as severe. According to the IMD, visibility also took a plunge and it was way below 200 metres. Kejriwal has also blamed the rising pollution levels on crop burning in adjoining states. Earlier, ambulance officers described the scene as a "horrific incident" and "scene of carnage". 
Photos from the scene show the car almost completely inside a classroom. There were 24 children aged between seven and 11 in the year three classroom at the time. 
Police said the car had left the road and crashed into the classroom inside a demountable weatherboard building. 
The incident took place inside the school grounds, with the driver suspected to have lost control of the vehicle while parking, or entering or exiting the school. 
One witness suggested the driver may have hit the accelerator when she meant to brake. Car slams into school in Sydney's west. Channel 9

NSW ambulance officers have described the scene at Banksia Road Primary School at Greenacre as "horrific". 
Emergency crews responded to reports of at least seven people injured at 9.45am, and arrived at the scene to find two in cardiac arrest and another in a serious condition.

posts.title: BREAKING NEWS: West Ham appoint Moyes to succeed sacked Bilic
posts.text:
7 Nov 2017, 9:11 - 
West Ham have appointed David Moyes as their new manager after sacking Slaven Bilic on Monday. 
Bilic had been under pressure for a while following an underwhelming start to the season, having received significant backing in the transfer market. 
The Croatian's final game in charge was Saturday's 4-1 hammering by Liverpool, a result that leaves the club in the relegation zone. 
Moyes - thought to be on a contract until the end of the season - is the man who has been tasked with getting West Ham out of their predicament, though his appointment has been met by a mixed response. 
The Scot publicly confirmed his interest in the job during a television appearance at the weekend, prompting some West Ham fans to air their disappointment at the prospect of him taking over. West Ham United can confirm the appointment of David Moyes as the Club's manager. pic.twitter.com/AIOWnHWn27 -- West Ham United (@WestHamUtd) November 7, 2017 
Upon the confirmation of his appointment, Moyes issued a rallying call to supporters. 
He said: "I'm really looking forward to the meeting the supporters, being in the stadium with them. 
"I'm looking forward to seeing them getting right behind the team and my team also. We need the support, we need everybody with us. 
"It's a big job we have in hand now but I'm sure with everybody together, we can get the right results between now and the end of the season." 
This is Moyes' first job in football since resigning from his post at Sunderland in May, having overseen the Black Cats' relegation to the Championship. 
Moyes also had unsuccessful spells in charge of Manchester United and Real Sociedad following an 11-year stint with Everton. 
He will now have the best part of two weeks to prepare West Ham for his first match in charge, with a trip to Watford up next after the international break - Moyes' 500th Premier League fixture. 
West Ham joint-chairman David Sullivan explained: "We need somebody with experience, knowledge of the Premier League and the players in it, and we believe David is the right man to turn things around and get the best out of the players at the club. 
"He is highly regarded and respected within the game, and will bring fresh ideas, organisation and enthusiasm. 
"He proved with Everton that he has great qualities and we feel that West Ham United is a club that will give David the platform to display those qualities again." Zucolotto is a friend and best man of the judge Sergio Moro and was an associate of an office with Rosangela Moro, wife of the judge. Paulo newspaper, Zucolotto's talks with Tacla Duran would involve easing the penalty and reducing the fine that the former Odebrecht lawyer would have to pay in an award-winning deal. 


In return, according to Duran, Zucolotto would be paid by means of box two. The money would be used to "care" for the people who would help him negotiate, according to a correspondence between the two that the former Odebrecht lawyer says he has in his files. 

Zucolotto denies the charges. The prosecutors cited by Tacla Duran claim that they do not even know Moro's friend. Judge Sergio Moro pronounced, in a note, on the Folha de S. Paulo report:

- the lawyer Carlos Zucoloto Jr. is my personal friend and I regret that his name is used by an accused fugitive and in an irresponsible journalistic matter to denigrate me; and

Curitiba, August 27, 2017. 
Sergio Fernando Moro 
Federal judge"

posts.title: Οικογενειακά Επιδόματα: Προχωράνε οι αιτήσεις -Πότε θα καταβληθεί η Δ’ δόση
posts.text:
Προγραμματισμένη για λίγο πριν τα Χριστούγεννα είναι η Δ’ δόση των οικογενειακών επιδομάτων και στον ΟΓΑ εργάζονται εντατικά προς αυτή την κατεύθυνση.

Σημειώστε ότι το Ειδικό Επίδομα Τρίτεκνων – Πολύτεκνων Οικογενειών εισέπραξαν στο πλαίσιο της πληρωμής Γ’ Τριμήνου 730.000 οικογένειες δικαιούχων, έναντι 716.975 το 2016 ενώ, από την προηγούμενη πληρωμή της Β’ δόσης 2017, ο ΟΓΑ επεξεργάστηκε επιπλέον 170.000 αιτήσεις.
Επίσης ο Οργανισμός έχει ήδη εκκαθαρίσει και συνολικά πληρώσει φέτος περισσότερες από 70.000 εκκρεμείς αιτήσεις. Πρόκειται για αιτήσεις κυρίως του 2016 και του 2015, αλλά και παλαιότερες, για τις οποίες οι δικαιούχοι δεν είχαν προσκομίσει τα απαραίτητα δικαιολογητικά ή αυτά που είχαν προσκομίσει ήταν ελλιπή.
Οι διασταυρώσεις συνεχίζονται, οι δικαιούχοι ενημερώνονται για την ανάγκη προσκόμισης τυχόν συμπληρωματικών δικαιολογητικών, ώστε να προχωρήσει περαιτέρω η εκκαθάριση εκκρεμών αιτήσεων ταυτόχρονα με την επεξεργασία των Α21 που υποβλήθηκαν μετά την 1 Οκτωβρίου 2017 και θα υποβάλλονται για το επόμενο διάστημα.
Για όσες αιτήσεις συνεχίζεται ο έλεγχος – λόγω και ελλιπών δικαιολογητικών – και για όσες υποβλήθηκαν ή θα υποβληθούν από 1 η Οκτωβρίου 2017 και μετά, η πληρωμή θα πραγματοποιηθεί με τη δόση του Δ’ τριμήνου (πριν τα Χριστούγεννα). 
Υπενθυμίζεται πως για το έτος 2017 οι δικαιούχοι μπορούν να υποβάλλουν αιτήσεις Α21 στην ΑΑΔΕ (σύστημα taxis) μέχρι και 15 Ιανουαρίου 2018. Ο ΟΓΑ θα ειδοποιήσει με ηλεκτρονικό ταχυδρομείο όσους πρέπει να προσκομίσουν συμπληρωματικά δικαιολογητικά, αλλά ταυτόχρονα καλεί όλους τους ενδιαφερόμενους να επισκεφτούν την ιστοσελίδα του (www.oga.gr, πεδίο «Πληροφορίες Αιτήσεων Οικογενειακών Επιδομάτων») προκειμένου να ενημερωθούν σχετικά.

posts.title: MIS LABIALES VIOLETA (SWATCHES Y REVIEW)
posts.text:
En el post de hoy quiero enseñaros una selección de cinco labiales en tono violeta que forman parte de mi colección de labiales. Así que si te gustan estas tonalidades para los labios ¡empezamos con los swatches! 

El primero que quiero enseñaros es el labial 819 Pearly Lavender de los Ultra Glossy Stylo de Kiko , un labial en un tono violeta muy clarito que tiene un efecto “gloss”. En un principio no me veía bien con un tono tan sumamente claro pero combinado con looks de ojos en tonos morados potentes me parece que es un acierto total. También es muy buena opción de labial para ponerlo encima de labiales de acabado mate a los que queramos dar ese efecto mojado (lo podéis ver en el swatch de la izquierda). 

Es hidratante y muy cómodo de llevar porque es muy cremosito pero es cierto que no tiene una gran duración en los labios. No obstante es un producto que no alcanzaba los 5 euros pero no estoy segura de que aún se puedan comprar en tiendas Kiko. 

El segundo labial violeta que os quiero destacar es el Viva Glam Ariana Grande 2 de Mac . A pesar de ser un labial de acabado mate se desliza muy bien por el labio y resulta muy cómodo de llevar. Se queda el acabado mate pero la sensación es casi la de llevar un labial cremoso. 

El tono me cuesta mucho que la cámara lo capte al cien por cien pero os puedo asegurar que es realmente bonito. Además, tiene muy buena cobertura y muy buena duración. Tiene un precio aproximado de 20 euros y, al ser un Viva Glam, todo lo recaudado por su compra va destinado a la ayuda contra el Sida. 

El siguiente labial es muy similar al anterior en cuanto a tonalidad. Es el labial Mystic de Sleek de la gama True Color . Es un labial morado con subtono violeta de acabado mate también. En este caso, al deslizarlo por el labio sí notamos esa textura un poco más seca que un labial cremoso pero nada que no sea confortable de llevar. 

Tiene muy buena pigmentación y una duración buena para ser un producto bastante económico, ya que ronda los 6 euros. Cuando se borra del labio se borra completamente sin dejar parches. 


Con el siguiente labial estoy más que encantada y creo que ya lo sabéis porque os los he recomendado mil veces. Éste es el tono 03 de los Color Fix de Deliplus , un color violeta - morado pero algo más intenso que los anteriores. 

Cuesta únicamente 3,50 euros y son de los labiales más fiables que he tenido. Su pigmentación es muy buena, su duración excelente incluso comiendo, cómodos de aplicar, de llevar… No le pongo ninguna pega. 

Y el quinto labial me consta que tira algo más hacia el fucsia (y más viéndolo al lado del resto de labiales), pero comparándolo con otros de la misma gama me tira un poco hacia el violeta también así que me vais a permitir que lo incluya en este post :) Es el Lip Tint de Bell en el tono 6 . A diferencia de los anteriores, éste es un tinte labial con una textura más líquida. Tenemos que tener algo de cuidado a la hora de maquillarnos porque puede escurrirse por los bordes del labio. Y también os recomendaría aplicar un par de capas para que quede más homogéneo el color y para darle algo más de intensidad, ya que son modulables. 

Algo muy bueno de este Lip Tint es que nos tiñe el labio, así que aunque vaya desapareciendo siempre nos dejará algo de color. Y finalmente os comento que tienen un precio low cost: más o menos 4 euros. 

Estos son los cinco primeros labiales en tonalidades violeta que hoy os quería enseñar. Y para las más atrevidas y que os gustan los tonos morados más potentes y evidentes, tranquilas que próximamente os enseñaré una nueva selección en el blog y en el canal, donde por supuesto podéis echar un vistazo ya mismo de cómo quedan todos los labiales aplicados. 


¿Cuál os ha hecho más ojitos? ¿Cuál destacaríais vosotras?  



Os dejo con el vídeo de youtube por si queréis ver todos estos labiales "en movimiento". 





  
Os recuerdo que podéis seguirme por Youtube (SwatchesEneri), FB ("Los swatches de Eneri"), Twitter (@SwatchesEneri) e Instagram ( http://instagram.com/swatcheseneri# ) donde actualizo con información que os puede resultar interesante.

Как получить Root на Pixel 2 XL с помощью Magisk (Инструкция) 07.11.2017 
Многие опытные пользователи Android покупают новые смартфоны Google Pixel не только из-за их мощной начинки и самой свежей версии операционной системы Android, но и в надежде на традиционно широкую поддержку устройств этой компании со стороны независимых производителей. 
И это действительно так: сегодня у нас есть хорошие новости для владельцев смартфонов Pixel 2 XL, получить Root на которых они могут с помощью Magisk. Причем сделать это будет достаточно несложно. 


Это стало возможным, благодаря выходу новой версии (14.4) Magisk, которая теперь поддерживает смартфоны Google Pixel 2 XL. Разработчик тестировал работу Magisk 14.4 со смартфоном, работающим под управлением сборки Android 8.0 OPD1.170816.010, но в теории он должен без каких-либо проблем работать и с более свежими версиями этой операционной системы, включая Android 8.1 beta. 

Еще одной хорошей новостью является то, что получить root на Pixel 2 XL с помощью Magisk можно не устанавливая на смартфон альтернативное рекавери и не подключая его к ПК: единственной вещью, которая потребуется — это Magisk и ничего кроме него. 

Что такое Magisk и как установить его на смартфон вы можете почитать в этом материале . Как получить root на Pixel 2 XL с помощью Magisk 

1. Запустите Magisk и на его главном экране выберите: «Установка» -> «Установить» -> «Пропатчить boot-образ». 

2. Magisk Manager внесет необходимые изменения в загрузочный образ вашего смартфона и сохранит его во встроенной памяти в папке /MagiskManager в виде файла patched_boot.img 

3. После установки пропатченного boot-образа перезагрузите ваш смартфон. 

Всё, теперь вы можете пользоваться root доступом на вашем смартфоне.

Agenda Plis Plas @PPdeVigo denuncia que el Gobierno local solo ha ejecutado el 5,6% del presupuesto de Educación 
  Portada , Vigo al día   
El Grupo Municipal del Partido Popular ha denunciado que en lo que va de año el Gobierno Municipal sólo ha ejecutado un 5,6% de las inversiones previstas en el área de Educación. Un “incumplimiento” en el que, la concelleira Teresa Egerique, ha destacado los 570.000€ “previstos para la cubrición de patios de colegios, de los que sólo se habían invertido, a 30 de septiembre, 21.074”. 
“Todo son anuncios que luego no se concretan”, ha detallado Egerique, quien ha lamentado que centros como el de Carballal, Virxe do Rocío o Canicouva sigan “esperando y exactamente igual”. 
En este escenario, la representante del PP ha analizado las previsiones que ofrecen las cuentas de 2018 en materia de Educación, “con todas las reservas que conlleva esta elevada falta de ejecución” . Unos presupuestos que, como detalla, vuelven a ignorar uno de los principales servicios municipales como es el de los accesos a los colegios. 
A este respecto, Egerique ha calificado de “accesos tercermundistas” los entornos que presentan centros como el República de Uruguay de Teis, el Párroco don Camilo en San Andrés, el Carlos Casares o el Ramón y Cajal. 
“Todos estos centros tienen serios problemas en sus accesos. Por lo tanto, creemos que ya es hora de que se incluya una partida para solucionar las dificultades diarias que sufren los padres y alumnos”, ha continuado Egerique, quien ha avanzado que, entre las enmiendas a los presupuestos que presentará su grupo, se incluirá una partida de 500.000€ destinada a la mejora de los accesos. 
La edil del PP ha criticado que las cuentas repitan una vez más partidas como la sala de lectura de Navia al tiempo que reducen “drásticamente” otras como el programa de actividades para la Biblioteca Neira Vilas o el programa Vigo Educa, que pasa de 60.000 a 21.000€. “Al alcalde no le interesan este tipo de iniciativas porque sólo benefician a los jóvenes, y no a él”. Bientôt une voie verte sur les berges de Seine à Orly © Fb Pré-chantier du tramway T9: travaux à Choisy 
Un tronçon de plus dans la voie de cheminement de la rive gauche de la Seine en Val-de-Marne. Sur près d’un kilomètre, une nouvelle voie verte va remplacer l’ancien chemin de halage à Orly. Elle sera complètement ouverte aux promeneurs dès le mois de décembre, pour des déplacements à pied et à vélo. 
Dans un second temps, le service des espaces verts et du paysage doit effectuer un travail important de génie végétal visant à notamment à protéger la berge du batillage. Jusqu’à présent, il fallait avoir le goût de l’aventure ou bien connaître les lieux pour emprunter les sentes le long des berges d’Orly. Cerné par un quartier résidentiel à Villeneuve-Le-Roi, plusieurs sites industriels ainsi que le port autonome, l’ancien chemin du halage servait parfois de dépotoir ou de piste pour quad et autres deux roues motorisés. Depuis le mois d’octobre, le Conseil départemental du Val-de-Marne y réalise une voie verte. « Sur environ 900 mètres, il y aura une bande de 1,40 mètres de sol stabilisé, puis un mélange terre-pierre de part et d’autre, qui sera ensuite végétalisé (au printemps), parfois sans l’intervention de l’homme. Des barrières seront disposées pour éviter le passage des engins motorisés mais seront assez espacées pour que les vélos puissent passer sans poser le pied par terre. Quelques bancs offriront des haltes aux promeneurs, et quelques placettes pavées viendront freiner la course des vélo » , détaille Véronique Lathière, paysagiste à la direction des espaces verts et paysages. Ce sont les services techniques de la ville d’Orly qui seront chargés de l’entretien de cet espace. 
Quelques sentes crées par les promeneurs pourront être utilisées par les cyclistes, qui devront faire un peu de place aux marcheurs. Cet aménagement va également accueillir l’itinéraire de l’Euro-véloroute n°3, la « Scandiberique », entre Trondheiml en Norvège à Saint-Jacques-de-Compostelle en Espagne. Le coût total de ces travaux qui doivent se terminer entre la fin du mois de novembre et le début du mois de décembre s’élève à 260 000€ dont une partie à été financée par la Région Île-de-France, et l’autre par le Conseil Départemental. Un espace protégé de 5 hectares aux portes de Paris 
A chaque passage d’un bateau sur la Seine, de puissantes vagues viennent cogner la berge, la grignotant petit à petit. Au cours des derniers mois, l’association Au fil de l’eau, a placé à quelques endroits stratégiques, notamment devant la plage d’Orly, des épis déflecteurs. « Ce n’est que provisoire. Après une étude d’impact environnemental, nous allons transformer la berge pour radoucir son profil. Ainsi, l’eau s’écoulera plus facilement. C’est un espace sur lequel nous n’avons encore jamais vraiment travaillé et il y a fort à faire. C’est le plus grand espace protégé du département avec environ 5 hectares cumulés ! Grâce à la pente très douce qui s’enfonce dans le lit du fleuve, nous observons des herbiers de nénuphars et de potamus sur les hauts fonds. Par conséquent, des libellules de grande rivières, une vingtaine d’espèces de poissons et d’oiseaux peuplent la zone», explique Franz Barth, chargé de projets à la Direction des Espaces Verts et Paysage du Conseil départemental . Ces travaux de protection de l’espace n’interviendront qu’après un lourd volet réglementaire à l’horizon 2018. Du nouveau pour la passerelle d’Ablon 
Trop étroite, gardes-corps trop bas, la passerelle d’Ablon qui fait la liaison avec Vigneux dans l’Essonne devrait évoluer dans les prochains mois pour un réaménagement pérenne. En attendant, une goulotte dans laquelle les cyclistes pourront placer leurs vélos va être installée pour en faciliter la traversée.

Tonga ready to make Blair pay over RLWC insult premium_icon by Christian Nicolussi 
ADAM Blair is about to find out how much of a man Jason Taumalolo is. 
The New Zealand forward all-but placed a target on his chest when he questioned Taumalolo's integrity after his switch to represent Tonga in the Rugby League World Cup. 
Taumalolo's North Queensland clubmate Michael Morgan has warned the Kiwis to expect the wrath of the 115kg wrecking ball in what shapes as the most explosive World Cup clash in history. 
The Daily Telegraph understands the pumped-up Tongans will do their best to silence the outspoken Blair in the early exchanges at a packed Waikato Stadium in Hamilton on Saturday. Adam Blair can expect some rough stuff from Tonga. (Photo by Kai Schwoerer/Getty Images) 
"You don't want to poke the bear, that's for sure. We saw that through this year,'' said Morgan, when asked about Blair's taunts of Taumalolo. 
"I spoke to him when he said he was thinking about (Tonga). 
"There's always talk about players leaving their country of heritage to play for a stronger nation because of money, but he's done the opposite and still been sprayed for it. 
"Both his parents are Tongans, he was born in New Zealand but played for them in the last World Cup. 
"It's good he's done it. It wouldn't have been easy. He's copped a lot of flak from it. 
"But it's been good for the tournament because that also had a part in Andrew Fifita doing the same thing. It's been good for the whole tournament and game of rugby league in general.'' 
There is more than Pacific pride at stake in this weekend's ding-dong battle. The winner has the potential to ensure a saloon passage to the final as they would not meet Morgan and Australia until the December 2 decider in Brisbane. 
But the Tongans have not forgotten, or forgiven, Blair's pre-tournament gibe at $10 million man Taumalolo. 
Taumalolo and Fifita, who was initially picked for the Kangaroos, declared on the eve of the Cup they would play for Tonga for just $30 a day. 
Blair let rip on New Zealand radio and accused Taumalolo - the best forward in rugby league - of not being "man enough'' to let Kiwis coach David Kidwell know of his decision. 
"You've got to be a man and own up to what you want to do," Blair told NewstalkZB last month. 
"If you were man enough, you'd make the phone call and tell them. At this stage, it feels like we've been let down a lot. So do we let them back in the team? 
"You're going to have to find some way to be able to trust them again, but does that cause issues and problems that we don't need?'' 
Taumalolo still has something to prove. (Photo by Anthony Au-Yeung/Getty Images) 

That interview has infuriated some in the Tongan camp who have made a point of discussing ways of singling out Blair. 
Tonga put 50 points on Scotland and then Samoa 32-18 on the weekend with the pre-match ceremonial dances one of the best rugby league scenes all year. 
Tonga also features Will Hopoate, Michael Jennings and Manu Ma'u, another top-shelf forward eligible for New Zealand. 
Should Tonga win, they will likely host Lebanon in Christchurch before meeting England or Papua New Guinea in a semi-final in Auckland. If they lose to the Kiwis, Tonga will meet Lebanon and then Australia in the semi-final. Related Items

Kesibukan pasangan sering kali jadi masalah dalam hubungan. Niat hati ingin menghabiskan waktu dengan pasangan, tetapi apa daya pacar sibuk sendiri dan akhirnya diam-diam menahan rasa kesal. Dalam masalah ini sering kali cowok jadi subjek yang disalahkan, atau memang kenyataannya cowok sering salah. Menghindari ngambeknya cewek saat mau ditinggal sibuk jadi tugas besar bagi cowok, nggak mudah dan nggak gampang, cowok perlu perhitungan dan usaha yang matang.
Jangan sampai, cewek ditinggal sendirian tanpa kejelasan sementara cowok sibuk dengan dunianya. Kamu sebagai cowok di posisi ini pantas untuk disalahkan. Bagaimana tidak? Rasa sayang dan rindu dimentahkan olehmu dengan kesibukan, hati siapa yang nggak sakit? Cewek yang sering curiga dengan perilaku cowok akan tambah curiga kalau ditinggal-tinggal tanpa kejelasan. Baiknya cowok sebelum menuju ke kesibukannya, lakukan beberapa hal di bawah ini biar cewek nggak ngambek.
1. Sebelum sibuk dengan duniamu, ajak cewekmu berinteraksi, biar dia merasa kalau dirinya tetap penting untukmu Janji deh, nanti kalau udah kelar kita dinner bareng via unsplash.com 
Menghadapi cewek itu susah-susah gampang. Susah kalau kamu tak mengerti maunya seperti apa. Tapi aslinya ya gampang kalau saja kamu tau satu celahnya saja. Seperti persoalan pembagian waktu dengan dia dan duniamu yang lain, yang sering kali berujung dengan kesalahpahaman.
Saat dia tak terima dengan kesibukanmu itu, kamu menganggap dirinya tak pengertian. Padahal dia memang hanya ingin lebih diperhatikan biar dianggap penting olehmu. Dan itu sesederhana, ajak dia berinteraksi seperti sekadar biarkan dia bercerita rencananya hari ini, atau sekedar ajak dia bercanda. Karena interaksi ini yang bisa buat dia sedikit lebih tenang sebelum kamu tinggal sibuk.
2. Berusaha dengan sekuat tenaga meyakinkan dia kalau kesibukanmu itu secara nggak langsung baik buat masa depan hubungan Percaya deh, kalau cowok sibuk itu baik buat ceweknya. Nggak melulu cuma main doang via unsplash.com 
Ada berbagai macam kesibukkan, ada sebagian yang harus ditinggalkan dan ada yang benar-benar harus segera dikerjakan. Cewek yang ngambek karena ditinggal sibuk harus ditanggapi dengan lunak, jangan marah apalagi melawannya. Jelaskan bahwa kesibukkanmu bukan main-main saja, melainkan ada kaitannya dengan masa depan kalian berdua. Semoga dia lantas bisa mengerti dengan baik deh.
3. Beri juga kebebasan cewekmu untuk melakukan kegiatan yang dia suka Kalau kamu sering dilarang atau sering jadi sasaran kekesalannya karena dia nggak suka kamu sibuk, baiknya lakukan sesuatu yang baik untuknya. Berikan dia kesempatan untuk bersibuk ria, usahakan cewekmu juga bisa sibuk tanpa laranganmu. Kalau sudah begini hubungan bisa dijalani dengan adil, nggak ada satu hal yang bikin timpang. Kamu yang pengen sibuk jadi nggak masalah, karena cewekmu sudah paham mesti melakukan hal lain daripada ngambek.
4. Bukan meminta izin, tapi saat ada acara dadakan alangkah baiknya kamu memberi tahu pacar, bukankah ini salah satu keterbukaan? Yang paling membuat para cowok bimbang adalah acara dadakan yang nggak bisa ditolak sementara pacar pasti marah kalau ditinggal. Daripada kamu bingung, baiknya sepakati sejak awal kalau kamu sering sibuk mendadak. Utarakan kesibukanmu dengan jelas, semisal ada pekerjaan yang mesti diselesaikan bicarakan dengannya dengan baik dan jujur.
5. Pastikan kamu mudah dihubungi dan sempat mengabari, biar cewekmu tak berpikir macam-macam lagi Jangan sampai susah dihubungi, kalau lengah bisa-bisa dia ngambek via unsplash.com 
Banyak pertengkaran dalam hubungan terjadi karena komunikasi yang buruk. Alih-alih menyibukkan diri dengan pekerjaan, karena nggak lihai kasih kabar malah jatuhnya berantem karena salah paham. Kamu juga harus ngerti kalau ponselmu harus selalu aktif karena cewek bakal kesal kalau sampai kamu nggak bisa dihubungin sementara kesibukkanmu nggak dijelaskan ke dia.
6. Entah main ke mana atau sibuk apa, pastikan jangan sebut nama cewek lain biar cewekmu ini nggak cemburu Jangan sebut nama cewek, meski orang yang kamu maksud itu temanmu via unsplash.com 
Kesibukkan cowok kadang memang mencurigakan. Entah main ke mana dan entah sedang sama siapa kadang dengan entengnya dia ninggalin cewek sendirian tanpa kejelasan. Kalau pun izin untuk main atau kesibukkan lainnya jangan sampai deh kamu sebut nama cewek, kalau kamu sampai menyebutnya kecurigaan cewek bakalan semakin menjadi-jadi. Kamu harus bijak dan cerdik.
7. Sibuk boleh, tapi kamu dan dia tetap harus punya jadwal quality time bersama Jadwal kerja selalu ada, jadwal main sam temen sudah disepakati bersama, tapi apa kabar jadwal quality time bareng pacar? Kamu kadang lupa kalau kalian butuh waktu bareng, menghabiskannya untuk hal-hal yang romantis. Mulai sekarang baiknya sepakati jadwal buat ketemu dan jalan-jalan biar hubungan tetap aman dan nyaman.
Cewek berhak buat marah karena cowok sering menghilang tanpa kejelasan, sebaliknya cowok harus bersabar kalau cewek sedang sibuk tanpa kejelasan. Cewek yang sibuk harus dimaklumi, cowok yang sibuk harus dicurigai, semua itu bisa dikatakan lumrah, meski dengan berat hati. Dalam hubungan perkara waktu adalah hal penting, waktu yang berkualitas nggak bisa didapat dengan mudah, harus dengan perencanaan dan kesepakatan biar sama-sama bisa menikmatinya. Semoga kalian diberi waktu longgar untuk berbalas romansa, kasih sayang dan rindu.

posts.text:
7 Nov 2017, 8:31 - 
People who have been tricked into transferring money to a fraudster could find it easier to get their money back under plans set out by a regulator. 
The Payment Systems Regulator (PSR) has been looking into such scams following a "super complaint" by consumer group Which? over concerns that, unlike many other payment methods, victims conned into transferring money by bank transfer to a fraudster have no legal right to get their money back from their bank. 
Plans outlined by the PSR, following work with the payments industry, aim to make it harder for fraudsters to commit such crimes, ensure banks follow best practice and help them to recover money. 
A reimbursement scheme has also been proposed, which could help people get their money back under certain circumstances - but the PSR said there is "no silver bullet" and some people will still lose out. Today, we have announced our progress on the work to tackle payment scams. You can read more here: https://t.co/IGliwhknAE 
-- PSR (@ThePSR) November 7, 2017 
New statistics published by UK Finance show that in the first six months of 2017 alone more than 19,000 victims were a target of the scams - known as authorised push payment (APP) scams - involving a total amount of over £100 million. 
The PSR said it is seeking feedback on how best to introduce a "contingent reimbursement model" by September 2018. 
The proposed model would set out the circumstances when victims of such scams would get their money back, and which bank or payment organisations should pay. 
Whether or not the fraud victim gets their money back would depend on whether banks and payment organisations had met required standards, including measures and processes that help prevent and respond to scams - as well as whether or not the victim has taken an appropriate level of care in protecting themselves. 
The PSR said the compensation model aims to help reinforce compliance with new best practice standards that banks will follow when a victim reports one of these scams. 
Hannah Nixon, managing director of the PSR, said the new measures will make a "positive difference" to scam victims and help prevent such frauds happening. 
She continued: "However, there is no silver bullet for APP scams and some people will still, unfortunately, lose out. That's why we've continued to look for a solution that could reimburse those who are scammed, and today we begin consulting on an option that we think could work. 
"To be successful, the model must be pragmatic: consumers will need to be vigilant and protect themselves, but equally we expect banks and payment service providers to uphold best practice - and when they don't there should be reimbursement." 
The report was welcomed by Which? 
Chief executive Peter Vicary-Smith said: "A year on from our super complaint, it's good to see the regulator coming down on the side of consumers. 
"If this stops the huge amounts of money lost to bank transfer scams, it'll be a significant win. 
"To make this a reality, the regulator must now ensure any reimbursement scheme properly compensates victims. Meanwhile, banks must move to quickly put in place better checks and protections to prevent these scams happening in the first place." 
The PSR said new protections to help prevent scams happening and help banks recover money faster will include: 
:: Confirmation of payee starting in 2018, allowing customers to verify that they are paying the person they intend.:: Transaction data analytics, starting in 2018, helping banks to shut down mule accounts taken over by criminals for fraudulent activity and spot potential fraudulent payments.:: "Know your customer" data sharing for banks due in 2020 to help stop fraudsters opening accounts they use for scams.:: Improved data sharing - providing a better understanding to help banks work together to respond to scams faster. 
The Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) said it had previously found that, generally, procedures for handling cases of push payment scams are often unclear and inconsistently applied. 
It said it will be actively monitoring the adoption, implementation and impact of the standards.

Semuanya Pakai Tarif Tunggal Ke depannya, pemerintah akan membuat golongan tersebut single price dan tidak ada lagi tarif golongan pada rumah tangga.   15:47 TribunBatam/Wahib Waffa Petugas PLN Tanjungpinang memperbaiki jaringan kabel di kawasan terbakar, Teladan 
TRIBUNBATAM.ID- Akan ada kebijakan baru terkait golongan pelanggan listrik PT PLN . 
Kementerian Energi dan Sumber Daya Mineral (ESDM) dan PT Perusahaan Listrik Negara (PLN) berencana menghapus kelas golongan pelanggan listrik Rumah Tangga (R-1) dari daftar golongan pelanggan tariff adjustment (non-subsidi). 
Menteri ESDM , Ignasius Jonan mengatakan, perihal penghapusan golongan ini akan dibicarakan dalam rapat bersama dengan PLN . 
Rencananya akan ada perubahan dari daftar golongan pelanggan tariff adjustment. 
Seperti diketahui, ada beberapa kelas golongan pelanggan PLN non-subsidi, yaitu golongan Rumah Tangga (R-1) 900 VA-RTM (Rumah Tangga Mampu), 1.300 VA, dan 2.200 VA. Adapun ketiga golongan itulah yang akan dihapuskan. 
"Bahkan PLN sudah sepakat untuk mengubah kelas golongan. Kelas golongan pelanggan rumah tangga, sekarang kan 450 VA, 900 VA, 1.300 VA, 2.200 VA. Kecuali yang menerima subsidi, yang lain sekalian 4.400 VA 13.200 VA," katanya di Kantor Bursa Efek Indonesia (BEI), Selasa (7/11/2017). 
Menurutnya, penghapusan kelas golongan pelanggan itu dilakukan karena jarak batas dayanya sangat kecil yakni 900 VA, 1.300 VA, dan 2.200 VA. 
Ia menginginkan kelas golongan pelanggan rumah tangga dijadikan satu saja. 
"Jadi tidak usah mepet-mepet kecil-kecil (batas dayanya)," ucap dia. 
Kepala Satuan Unit Komunikasi Korporat PLN , I Made Suprateka membenarkan bahwa akan ada perubahan daftar golongan pelanggan tariff adjustment. 
Dalam daftar tariff adjustment, golongan Rumah Tangga (R-1) terdiri dari batas daya 900 VA, 1.300 VA, dan 2.200 VA dengan harga pemakaian per kWh berbeda-beda. 
Ke depannya, pemerintah akan membuat golongan tersebut single price. 
"Maksudnya tidak ada lagi golongan-golongan itu. Jadi semua harga sama untuk semua golongan," pungkasnya. (kontan/Pratama Guitarra)

Huawei Honor V10 получит безрамочный дисплей, сдвоенную камеру и фирменный процессор Kirin 970 07.11.2017 
Всемирно известный производитель телекоммуникационного оборудования и мобильных устройств, компания Huawei продолжает наращивать и без того достаточно обширный арсенал выпускаемых ею смартфонов. 
В дополнение ко всем новинкам, представленным этой компанией в нынешнем году, вскоре нам стоит ожидать появления очередного смартфона — Huawei Honor V10. Что нам на этот раз хотят предложить? 

А хотят предложить нам смартфон, оснащенный особо модным в этом году дисплеем вытянутой в длину формы с размером 5.99 дюймов по диагонали и разрешением сторон 18:9, занимающий чуть ли не всю площадь передней панели, и фирменным процессором Huawei: чипом Kirin 970. 

Согласно имеющимся на сегодняшний день сведениям, начинка Honor V10 будет также включать в себя как минимум 6 ГБ оперативной памяти, от 64 до 128 ГБ встроенной флеш-памяти и сдвоенную основную камеру, выполненную на базе 16 и 2-мегапиксельных сенсоров. 

Работать новинка будет под управлением самой свежей на сегодня версии операционной системы Google: Android 8.0, поверх которой будет традиционно установлена фирменная оболочка EMUI 6.0. 

Это все, что пока нам известно о Huawei Honor V10., но появления полных сведений об этом смартфоне нам не придется слишком долго ждать: презентация новинки состоится 5 декабря нынешнего, 2017 года на специально созванном для этого мероприятии в Европе.

posts.text:
Outback Creative moves ahead with online brokerage platform 7th Nov 2017 4:48 PM B Carige in Sarah Warner's Sunburnt Country image. Sarah Warner Photography by Andrea Davy Andrea Davy Journalist I come from a family of proud stockmen and when I was younger my weekends and school holidays where always filled with riding horses and mustering cattle. There isn’t a job I would rather be doing. There are not too many jobs where you learn something new every day. I have struck a good balance in Mackay and I love that I can work at the busy newspaper and I still have time to compete at Campdrafts on the weekends. I am still a country girl at heart and I think Mackay still feels that little... Login to follow 
IT'S gone from a daydream to a reality. 
This January, Outback Creative will go live with its online brokerage platform, making it a one-stop shop for the sale of rural Australian art to a large national and international market. 
When the founder of the initiative, Ranald McMaster, last caught up with the Rural Weekly he was juggling full-time work as a farmhand while co-ordinating the forum's newly released website and Facebook page. 
Since then, he has thrown in the day job, found a company partner and secured an investor. Outback Creative will publish its first book before Christmas and the launch of its online-selling platform by January 1 is well under way. 
He is watching his dreams for Outback Creative come to fruition, but Ranald admitted much of the hard work was still ahead of him. 
"I knew this wasn't going to be easy. There have been a lot of challenges, but I just bit the bullet and decided to go after it,” he said. 
"By next year we should be firing with all cylinders and growing rapidly and, hopefully, be trading a lot of art.” 
This year, Ranald, along with company partner Charles Devine, who is also a Goondiwindi lad, secured an investor that helped the business develop quickly. 
"The main change happening is we are transitioning from a business that was just doing purely exposure to a company now doing brokerage and publication,” he said. 
"So we are doing online brokerage... it's online sales of premium rural and indigenous arts; as a loose term we call it outback art, so it covers rural, nature, landscape, wildlife and indigenous art.” 
The artwork encompasses everything from poetry about years gone by and paintings of native birds to striking photos shot out of a helicopters above the Kimberley in Western Australia. Photos View Photo Gallery 
Most of the pieces carry a soft undertone of country Australia, and there are many images championing agriculture and rural families. 
"We want to get as much scope as possible, especially with our photography. We want to cover the whole of Australia,” he said. 
While all artists are encouraged to get in touch with Outback Creative to suggest their work, Ranald explained they were highly selective about choosing which artists to back. 
"It's very much an invite-only exclusive opportunity,” he said. 
"We run a community group on Facebook, which is for everyone. 
"We are all about encouraging everyone, but we want to have a gold standard of art for people to aspire to and to purchase.” 
He said supporting indigenous artists was deeply important to Outback Creative. 
"We have a lease arrangement with Aboriginal Artlandish as a strategic alliance to try and bolster up the numbers,” he said. 
"Indigenous art covers a lot of different sub-genres, including Aboriginal artefacts like didgeridoos. 
"We want a strong representation of indigenous artists on board, that's a market we want to take by storm.” 
Outback Creative 's book, which will be published at the end of the year, will be on a print run of about 2,500 copies. 
Ranald said the venture was to test the water to see what demand was like for a product of that kind. 
The book will be full of the best rural images, accompanied by poetry from Mick Martin. 
Mick is heavily involved with Outback Creative and is in charge of co-ordinating content for its social-media platforms. 
Now, all day every day, Ranald is working with art. 
This has been his dream from the beginning, but he admitted pursuing it was a leap of faith. 
Forfeiting a wage was only made easier by the support of his family. 
"I felt like this was my chance and I couldn't let it slip,” he said. 
"It was time for me to do something that made my heart sing. 
"Securing our investor gave us some breathing room... but further government support may be needed.” 
Outback Creative 
WE MAY find pictures taken that remind of things we've had 
and art that makes us happy and a few that makes us sad. 
The spot down by the river where old Granddad used to sit 
or bridles on the railing where young horses learned the bit. 
Collages, stark and subtle, watercolours soft and sweet. 
Those time-exposure pictures of the growing fields of wheat. 
Hot sunsets' ruby colours on the skies of smoky red. 
Poor calves of starving heifers where they lay, so sad, near dead. 
The artist, like the poet, has no place to pick and choose, 
the lens, the brush, so mirrored, like the writer finds their muse. 
This outback is creative, more than anyone can claim 
but here the brush and camera put her firmly in the frame. 
We feel the truth of artists 'neath these Aussie candid skies 
and share the many wonders through the skilful artist's eyes. 
Poem by Mick Martin

Chị Nguyễn Thị Hải Yến, cán bộ mảng chính sách xã hội của UBND xã Kỳ Hải cho biết, trong số những hộ gia đình đang sinh sống trên địa bàn xã, có 16 gia đình có hoàn cảnh đặc biệt khó khăn. Hầu hết họ đều là phụ nữ, người già và trẻ nhỏ đang sinh sống trong những ngôi nhà lụp xụp nên khi thiên tai xảy ra, cuộc sống của họ càng lâm vào bế tắc.
Đến nay, phần lớn những gia đình này mới chỉ khắc phục tạm thời những hư hỏng, thiệt hại để ổn định cuộc sống, về lâu dài, họ vẫn cần sự hỗ trợ từ cộng đồng để gia cố nhà cửa, chống chọi với thiên tai. Không chỉ mang đến vô vàn khó khăn cho người dân, thiên tai còn tàn phá hàng loạt công trình hạ tầng với con số thiệt hại lên tới hàng nghìn tỷ đồng. Trường học, trạm y tế, công trình dân sinh...ở nhiều nơi hư hỏng nặng nề, rất cần nguồn lực để khắc phục.
Tiếng gọi từ vùng bão đã thôi thúc nhiều tổ chức cộng đồng và các doanh nghiệp thực hiện những chương trình an sinh xã hội nhằm sẻ chia gian khó, xoa dịu những nỗi đau, trong đó có Prudential. Vào trung tuần tháng 10, doanh nghiệp này đã tổ chức buổi thăm hỏi, trao quà tặng cho người dân các địa phương chịu thiệt hại nặng nề sau bão số 10 tại tỉnh Hà Tĩnh. Dù chưa hết ám ảnh về sự tàn phá của thiên tai và những khó khăn chồng chất sau đó, những người dân vùng bão Hà Tĩnh cũng cảm thấy ấm lòng khi đón nhận những tình cảm, sự sẻ chia của doanh nghiệp.
Về với vùng bão Hà Tĩnh trong những chuyến đồng hành khắc phục hậu quả thiên tai, Prudential còn đóng góp số tiền 50 triệu đồng giúp trường THPT Kỳ Lâm (huyện Kỳ Anh) sửa chữa cơ sở vật chất bị hư hỏng do bão. Đây là ngôi trường dành cho học sinh 5 xã vùng thượng Kỳ Anh, nơi vừa chịu những ảnh hưởng rất lớn cả về nhà cửa cũng như những cánh rừng nguyên liệu mà mỗi gia đình đã trồng, chăm sóc nhiều năm qua.
Được biết, tất cả những hoạt động trên nằm trong khuôn khổ chương trình “Hỗ trợ phòng tránh và giảm thiểu rủi ro thiên tai” do Prudential Việt Nam phối hợp với Tổng Cục Phòng chống Thiên tai (Bộ NNPTNN) và Quỹ Hỗ trợ Phòng tránh Thiên tai miền Trung thực hiện. Trong khi Prudential đang nỗ lực triển khai chương trình tại các tỉnh miền Trung nhằm khắc phục hậu quả do bão số 10, cơn bão số 11 cũng đã đi vào đất liền và đang “hoành hành” tại các tỉnh miền núi phía Bắc.

Our goal has always been to address the pain points of our customers and to make AccountSight the easiest and most convenient time tracking and billing software to use. CUPERTINO, CA, November 07, 2017 /24-7PressRelease/ -- AccountSight has been identified as a top five most simple to use time tracking software, based on hundreds of reviews on time tracking apps from real users like yourself, with data collected on aspects such as Ease of Use and Ease of Setup on G2 Crowd. G2 Crowd, the world's leading business solution review platform, leverages more than 250,000 user reviews to drive better purchasing decisions. Business professionals, buyers, investors, and analysts use the site to compare and select the best software and services based on peer reviews and synthesized social data. Every month, nearly one million people visit G2 Crowd's site to gain unique insights. G2 Crowd aims to bring authenticity and transparency to the business marketplace. AccountSight ranked at the top of three satisfaction categories. It scored a ninety-nine percent Ease of Use, a ninety-seven percent Ease of Admin and a ninety-five percent Ease of Setup. AccountSight has 15 reviews overall and was named a High Performer in the most recent G2 Crowd Time Tracking Grid Report. To learn more, check out the AccountSight reviews page on G2 Crowd. "It is a great honor to be selected in the top simple to use category by G2Crowd," said Mahender Bist, CEO of AccountSight. "Our goal has always been to address the pain points of our customers and to make AccountSight the easiest and most convenient time tracking and billing software to use. This validates our development approach to creating a more user-friendly software in the marketplace". AccountSight time and billing software has the following features: - Easy time tracking and expense tracking. - Efficient timesheet and expense approval workflow notifications. - Resource planning for future projects. - Time off module with multiple calendars for employees and consultants. - QuickBooks and PayPal integration. - Fast and easy manual and recurring online invoicing. - Configurable automatic reminders on timesheet, expense and invoices. - Quick and professional project estimates for bidding. - Powerful dashboards and reports for online project management and invoice status. - Drill-down directly from dashboards into time, expenses and invoicing reports. AccountSight offers a free 30 day trial to see how it can help your company save time and money and increase employee productivity. There is no credit card needed. Companies can utilize the free trial at https://www.accountsight.com/ . System Requirements: AccountSight works with any operating system. Supported browsers are Internet Explorer, Mozilla Firefox, Google Chrome and Safari. Pricing: AccountSight is a subscription based software with prices starting from $8 to $10/user. Volume discounts available for larger companies and government organizations. Please contact AccountSight directly for special pricing.About AccountSight: AccountSight is a leading time tracking and invoicing software that is integrated with QuickBooks, eSign Genie and PayPal. It is easy to use with comprehensive features and ideal for small to big companies. It is full of productivity-driven features that are conveniently available to users through a very helpful interface. The exceptional customer service as well as the many customer benefits make AccountSight the perfect choice for companies who need a convenient and cost-effective time tracking, resource planning and billing solution. For more information, please visit https://www.accountsight.com/ . # # #

posts.text:
JLT MT2010. Защищенный по военным стандартам планшет с операционной системой Windows 10 на борту 07.11.2017 
В сегменте рынка планшетов, способных работать в экстремальных условиях очередное пополнение: здесь появился новый Windows планшет, сертифицированный на соответствие военному стандарту MIL-STD-810G. 
Это означает, что новинка получившая наименование JLT MT2010 имеет пыле и водонепроницаемый ( IP65 ) корпус, способна выдерживать температуры в диапазоне от -10 до +50°C и падения с высоты 1.2 метра. 

Внутри защищенного корпуса вы найдете четырехъядерный процессор Intel Celeron N2930 работающий на частоте 1.83 ГГц, от 4 ГБ до 8 ГБ оперативной памяти типа LPDDR3 и SSD (MLC) накопитель с емкостью от 64 до 256 ГБ. 

Дисплей планшета JLT MT2010, который имеет размер 10.1 дюйма по диагонали и разрешение Full HD, может похвастаться достаточно высокой для работы под прямым солнечным светом яркостью, а его аккумулятор имеющий емкость 10280 мАч обеспечит новинке длительное время автономной работы. 
За коммуникационные возможности в новом планшете отвечает набор из беспроводных Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Bluetooth 4.1 и 4G LTE (опционално) модулей, док-порт, порт для модулей расширений, разъемы DV, и аудио, Giga-LAN, microHDMI (опционально) выход и USB 3.0 порт. 

Основная камера новинки имеет разрешение 5 мегапикселей, а на её передней панели размещена 2-Мп веб-камера. 
Больше подробностей о планшете вы найдете на сайте его производителя.
